issue.body:
**Description**: 
In ONNX opset 14, CumSum adds support for input/output data type MLFloat16 and BFloat16. (See https://github.com/onnx/onnx/commit/bc7a70b46f4ae88383a4ca49c477fd859715620c)

Here we enable MLFloat16 for CumSum, and omit BFloat16 for now.

**Motivation and Context**
- Why is this change required? What problem does it solve?
- If it fixes an open issue, please link to the issue here.
